data.description: MOVE IN READY! This immaculate home is located in the sought after Tamarron Community. Featuring 4 bedrooms 3 1/2 bath with a gameroom for your family to enjoy. Have Furr babies? No problem, this large backyard has plenty of space for your pups to play and/or for your kiddos to run around in. Also equipped, with a large kitchen with plenty of entertainment space for friends and family to enjoy a home cook meal.     Schedule your appointment today to take a look at your new home!
